ube.com%2Fc%2FPomato%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E8%258C%2584&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=ee24bbb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/Pomato%E5%B0%8F%E8%96%AF%E8%8C%84</a><br />\n<br />\nFH production：<a href=\"https://youtube.com/c/FHProductionHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fc%2FFHProductionHK&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=b7e8303d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/FHProductionHK</a><br />\n<br />\nArm Channel: <a href=\"https://youtube.com/c/ArmChannelTV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fc%2FArmChannelTV&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=2affc2e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/ArmChannelTV</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好話咩兩害取其輕、票投泛民嚟比喻睇ViuTV唔睇CCTVB，當年泛民起碼都無聯署撐國安法，ViuTV老闆李澤楷有<br />\n<br />\n李澤楷仲要喺未有國安法之前主動抽起王丹、馮敬恩嗰集《跟著矛盾去旅行》、聘請同中聯辦關係密切嘅陳鐵彪掌管新聞部<br />\n<br />\n無錯，上面D channel同VIUTV一樣都有賣藍店廣告，但起碼無聯署撐國安法，無自我審查抽起節目，甚至勇敢表態，蘋果嘅老闆黎智英甚至被政權逼害陷於冤獄<br />\n<br />\n就算你睇ViuTV我都唔會批鬥你，從來都係優先次序，唔係話睇咗就要批鬥：<br />\n<br />\n黃channel &gt; ViuTV &gt; TVB &gt; 支那綜藝&gt;黨台/CCTV<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好講到唔睇ViuTV就要睇「開心大綜藝」、講到睇ViuTV係抵制TVB唯一方法咁<br />\n<br />\n另外建議大家除左Netflix之外都支持下本地創作，否則香港語言、文化就快消亡"},{"pid":"df4c90144a20c522c8c352b6f15a431f9b8b7435","tid":2515972,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"毛記電視：<a href=\"https://youtube.com/c/%E6%AF%9B%E8%A8%98%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fc%2F%25E6%25AF%259B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596HK&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=5708ed81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/c/%E6%AF%9B%E8%A8%98%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96HK</a>"},{"pid":"9caa0ac498c973035fe343084b7988c35ee7fd3f","tid":2515972,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-